A cyberpunk-style digital illustration showing a lone figure in a dark, neon-lit room surrounded by translucent holographic screens displaying cascading streams of data packets and network traffic. The figure wears a glowing visor while manipulating floating 3D wireframe layers that stack vertically like archaeological dig sites, each layer revealing different colored data flows beneath. Electric blue and magenta light traces flow between the layers like visible network connections. The scene has a moody atmosphere with deep shadows, rain-streaked windows in the background reflecting city lights, and the characteristic cyberpunk aesthetic of high-tech surveillance meeting digital exploration. Small floating envelope icons drift through the data streams, subtly suggesting electronic communication being dissected and analyzed.
